        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4134641756" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15891044932009882575">Eight stories recreating the events of the 1989 Tiananmen Square via interviews, witness accounts and research; and how the ruling govt, Communist Party reinvented China, post-1989, using info suppression, disinformation, and propaganda tools. It stumps you more than any Orwell books ever could. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


