<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/49203415-we-have-been-harmonized"><img alt="We Have Been Harmonized: Life in China&#39;s Surveillance State" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1592247418l/49203415._SX98_.jpg" />
